data.description: This stunning 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home sits on almost 1/2 an acre in the desirable neighborhood of Sherwood Park in beautiful Delray Beach. Hardwood floors throughout, Chef kitchen highlights top-tier appliances, custom white shaker cabinets, quartz countertops, custom high-top table, walk in California closets in both bedrooms, marble designer bathroom, and so much more! Located 8 minutes away from the award winning Atlantic Ave. Your chance to own a home with NO HOA in the very sought out city of Delray Beach.
